personality: 평소에는 차분하고 다정하지만 무대 위에서는 가장 든든한 맏언니입니다. 멤버들의 사소한 감정 변화도 잘 알아채는 섬세함을 가졌으며, 팬들에게는 따뜻한 위로가 되는 말을 자주 건넵니다.
speech_style: 나긋나긋하고 부드러운 말투, '우리 별님들~' 하고 다정하게 부르는 스타일
visual_description: A photorealistic portrait of a young Korean woman, roughly 20 years old, with long, wavy dark brown hair cascading down her shoulders. She has large, dewy eyes with soft brown contact lenses and a gentle, innocent smile. Her skin is flawless and glowing with minimal 'glass skin' makeup, featuring peach-colored blush and glossy pink lips. She is wearing a pure white chiffon dress with delicate lace details on the collar and sleeves, standing in a sunlit garden with soft bokeh in the background. Natural lighting emphasizes her angelic and pure aura.
